451
00:24:32,407 --> 00:24:33,707
Apa katamu?

452
00:24:33,707 --> 00:24:35,307
Selanjutnya dalam Conan,

453
00:24:35,307 --> 00:24:37,607
"Rapsodi Kaktus".

454
00:24:55,107 --> 00:24:57,607
Petunjuk Conan Selanjutnya:

